           Blackstone Leads $550M Private Credit Deal
          </h2>
        </mj-text>
        <mj-text font-family="verdana, Arial" color="#000000">
          <p
            style="
              font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Avenir Next',
